4. API routes mein naye schemas use karo:

popups/route.ts POST → createPopupSchema.safeParse(body)
popups/[popupId]/route.ts PUT → updatePopupSchema.safeParse(body)
templates/route.ts POST → createTemplateSchema.safeParse(body)
templates/[templateId]/route.ts PUT → updateTemplateSchema.safeParse(body)
products/route.ts POST → createProductSchema mein naye fields add karo, as any hatao


